{"title":"秋收的前奏","authors":["木青"],"dates":[{"year":1963,"month":10,"day":17}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"秋收的前奏"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"木青"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"河边磨镰"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"河边青石上，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"磨镰霍霍响，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"个个小伙儿，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"浑身劲儿"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一早就憋的慌！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"磨！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"甩开膀子晃，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"磨得刀明光、湛亮，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"举眼前，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"映出一副笑脸膛！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"笑脸膛，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"再望那片好庄稼，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"心里更痒痒。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"恨不得七喳咔喳，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"先试试臂膀！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"队长啊，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"就等你话音响，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"这伙老虎，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"瞧吧，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"可着量往前闯。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"月亮地"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"明月高照，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"大队部正热闹，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"支部会刚开过，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"道上人影绰绰。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"夜静，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"狗不咬，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"只听得路上，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"几声朗朗笑！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"朗朗笑，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"有人把喀唠："},{"type":"paragraph","text":"“会开得好利索，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"秋收劲儿早鼓饱！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"明儿个开割，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"那时人欢马又叫！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"可有些事儿，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你可注意到？”"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"队长皱皱眉，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"把头摇了摇，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"“老支书，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你指的是秋收准备？"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"那不早……”"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"支书挥挥手："},{"type":"paragraph","text":"“我是说，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"小周有病要买药；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"李福媳妇要临产；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"老爷子也要动镰刀……"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"这一桩桩，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你可都想到？”"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"“哎呀，我的书记，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你真是婆婆佬，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"妥妥妥，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一定安排好！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"可有一件儿，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"实在管不了，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"六十多岁的老爷子，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"硬是不肯歇歇脚，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"说是公社丰收，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"干吗非让他们闲着！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"说我死心眼儿，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"不好不把他们瞧！”"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"明月高照，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"月下闪出毛毛道，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"队长和支书，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一边唠一边笑……"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":6,"page_end":6}